rComments: One of the best profs I ever had.  Great lectures and a great spirit in the classroom.  You really feel like she has taken the time to write an excellent lecture and wants you to do well too.  Highly recommended.
One of the best profs I've ever had.  Superb lecturer and able seminar leader.  I recommend all her courses.

Airhart false persona makes me sick. She pretends to care, when really she grades solely on preconceived biases towards people. She is totally unfair, and even worse- her lectures are truly awful. By the end of the term, every time she said, 'um' with her fake, girlish smile, I wanted to scream. Awful.
Fantastic teacher, concerned about making the course valuable for her students.
